RNMENT 控制<br />\n而且更加係猶太人主動加速種族融合 消滅白人"},{"pid":"835649c0ae09ab65681d9b530b11f7c87d95c2ae","tid":2530193,"uid":209662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"只有侵侵可以維持世界和平"},{"pid":"0f0621b41293e3bbda3ed9a42b6d08a3625b1d34","tid":2530193,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ae636adc8e01e8839113b1b6b986a73dc6bf96e","tid":2530193,"uid":270220,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4884fcace9bbe86b32daaa4b32cf2aaf72b8561a","tid":2530193,"uid":25424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:12:15.000Z","msg":"班猶太佬金主係咪支持民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"主要Progressive 反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過支持以色列嘅猶太人自己都攞嚟衰，踢走侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"呢個咁就幫佢哋唔到喇 反正佢哋自己單打巴勒斯坦人都已經足夠<br />\n<br />\n侵侵已經幫到盡"},{"pid":"837725670ee9657a68a8d071e9d829aa5f53e02a","tid":2530193,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"835649c0ae09ab65681d9b530b11f7c87d95c2ae","tid":2530193,"uid":209662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"只有侵侵可以維持世界和平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"不過佢亦同時都唔希望用戰爭模式去達至世界和平<br />\n結果就得罪咗美國軍方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要和平就要準備戰爭"},{"pid":"425d7c552328a3a35271556cd3d28b3cb878d80e","tid":2530193,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"Push 3"},{"pid":"42950ef31199bbddcce46eb833d9c9c7f0ee23e1","tid":2530193,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"Push 4"},{"pid":"19eac51d35bb94281667d068fb0d92bb53f315ec","tid":2530193,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c252484f19a68b10ae90a39004afc3c37b0a2bfd","tid":2530193,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/7C29D953-A2FF-4AE1-889D-05416382040F_w408_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F7C29D953-A2FF-4AE1-889D-05416382040F_w408_r1_s.jpg&h=e9582987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一枚以色列導彈向加沙市一座建築飛落而來。(2021年5月12日)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾十年來，美國外交政策的一個基石性的原則是毫不動搖地在政治上支持以色列。<br />\n但是本星期，在巴勒斯坦激進分子和以色列部隊發生的最新衝突之際，裂痕開始出現。這次衝​突是2014年以來以色列與哈馬斯組織之間最激烈的戰鬥。一些美國民主黨議員對以色列襲擊加沙地帶的哈馬斯表示了不滿，而共和黨人則繼續團結堅定地支持這個猶太國家。以色列對加沙的襲擊打死了至少83人，哈馬斯的火箭襲擊在以色列至少打死了六人。<br />\n白宮官員說，美國官員最近幾天與以色列、巴勒斯坦人以及該地區阿拉伯國家的領導人通話超過25次，試圖平息衝突。美國向以色列派出了一名特使，以斡旋停火。<br />\n美國總統喬&middot;拜登(Joe Biden)與以色列總理本傑明&middot;內塔尼亞胡(Benjamin Netanyahu)通了話。拜登後來說：&ldquo;我的預期和希望是，這會更早而不是更遲平息下來。當幾百枚火箭飛向你的國家時，以色列有權自衛。&ldquo;<br />\n拜登拒絕批評以色列的行動，但是白宮表示，拜登在與內塔尼亞胡交談時說，他相信，耶路撒冷城對世界各地信徒都如此重要，&ldquo;必須是和平之地&rdquo;。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-retains-its-support-for-israel-but-fissure-emerge-20210513/5890278.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fus-retains-its-support-for-israel-but-fissure-emerge-20210513%2F5890278.html&d=z1Z9%2FhyuGVbDXJZ%2FGqhOoRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=a97df77e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-retains-its-support-for-israel-but-fissure-emerge-20210513/5890278.html</a>"},{"pid":"e02ce84b5b27ec846025a86d2691eb1983c440b6","tid":2530193,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:19:56.000Z","msg":"Push 5"},{"pid":"0338495838a1cc75a2922020ce45c0747a4c663b","tid":2530193,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:21:17.000Z","msg":"Push 6"},{"pid":"f6050029cbd96ae30e4502c1a5470c60747bf26a"